item.title: CVE-2023-0506|2024-08-02T05:17:49.033Z -- bydemes%20group -- airspace%20cctv%20web%20service
item.description: The web service of ByDemes Group Airspace CCTV Web Service in its 2.616.BY00.11 version, contains a privilege escalation vulnerability, detected in the Camera Control Panel, whose exploitation could allow a low-privileged attacker to gain administrator access.
